{"tid":757083,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"新手玩Fortnite真係好難玩啊！","createTime":"2018-07-26T13:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T00:38:04.000Z","uid":33154,"like":40,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6c588894312f692f5dfb6b37bdde003b048187","tid":757083,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"之前玩PUBG都唔覺得<br />\n前排Down左隻Fortnite黎玩<br />\n先唔講佢d槍同資源有幾複雜<br />\n行左陣見到條友<br />\n諗住同佢對槍<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母佢一秒起左成座高樓大廈出黎圍住自己<br />\n打撚啊？<br />\n<br />\n我未玩之前都知呢隻Game有得起野<br />\n但新手點起得咁快啊<br />\n<br />\n玩左十幾場<br />\n用左一個鐘<br />\n場場都見到人就死<br />\n又或者未見到人就死<br />\n<br />\n你玩埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7181827482e30e408397d5dfbb6094b7fc42381","tid":757083,"uid":51989,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6240967c1cb42831ad46d57397452a3e8e774ae4","tid":757083,"uid":58140,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"隻game好蝦新手玩 <br />\n一係一班朋友玩"},{"pid":"88be5356c6d4045bb55f3d5d779c0f7d78ff3a70","tid":757083,"uid":152414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"依家有playground mode 自己可以練起嘢<br />\nKey bond 要自己set <br />\n睇多啲pro <br />\n以前我都覺得好難玩<br />\n玩咗個幾月先開始熟手<br />\n係咁 慢慢嚟就ok"},{"pid":"59fb7d263480f98a5be84c015e3d4930e4b374bb","tid":757083,"uid":152414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88be5356c6d4045bb55f3d5d779c0f7d78ff3a70","tid":757083,"uid":152414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"依家有playground mode 自己可以練起嘢<br />\nKey bond 要自己set <br />\n睇多啲pro <br />\n以前我都覺得好難玩<br />\n玩咗個幾月先開始熟手<br />\n係咁 慢慢嚟就ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"keybind*"},{"pid":"e413c2f370963efbc93ea611ba01097c52a3f3ed","tid":757083,"uid":150609,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score"